    <string name="quinoa_salad_instruction_4">4. In a small bowl, whisk together the lemon juice and olive oil</string>
    <string name="quinoa_salad_instruction_5">5. Pour the dressing over the quinoa mixture, and toss to combine</string>
    <string name="quinoa_salad_instruction_6">6. Season with salt and pepper to taste</string>

